h_wlan_2_54_130_300="<P>Mode<P>Select the desired wireless mode. The options are:<UL><LI>Up to 54 Mbps - Legacy Mode with maximum speed of up to 54 Mbps for b/g networks.<LI>Up to 217 Mbps - Neighbor Friendly Mode, with a speed up to 217 Mbps in presence of neighboring wireless networks.<LI>Up to 450 Mbps - Performance Mode - Maximum Wireless-N speed up to 450 Mbps. </LI></UL><P>The 2.4GHz (b/g/n) default is <b>Up to 217Mbps</b>, which allows all 11b and 11g and 11n wireless stations. The 5GHz (a/n) default is <b>Up to 450Mbps</b>, which allows all 11a and 11n wireless stations. </P>"
